function! Folds()
	" https://www.linux.com/training-tutorials/vim-tips-folding-fun/
	" close and open all folds: zi
	" open a fold und subfolds: zO
	" close a fold: zc
	" for pyhton use foldmethod=indent, otherweise fold method=syntax
